<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Formulario de Aportes</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #7daedc;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .form-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #000000;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #cccccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #cccccc;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #bbbbbb;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="form-container">

        <p>Registre tres formas en las que usted le aportar√≠a al mundo</p>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Forma 1">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Forma 2">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Forma 3">
        <br>
        <button>Guardar aporte</button>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
